replies.body:
Since Hextech Crafting is on a separate server than everything else you access in the client, it's often an unstable connection that causes issues accessing Hextech Crafting. When a connection drops before reaching the Hextech Crafting servers, the client is unsure of what to display, which is why you see a black  screen. The most common solutions can be found in our [connection guide. 
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Please let me know if you continue to see this issue after taking the steps in the guide.
